title: Fingerprint not working
content:
Fingerprint scanner to unlock phone (Pixel 3) fails most of the time, has about a 10% success rate, based on multiple fingers as well (left and right).   Tried wiping it out and recreating the saved fingers as well.

I have the switch parental controls app, and it's locked with fingerprint.  And it unlocks at a better succes rate.  So it's wierd.
